{"tid":1477551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重要！收音機疑接收大量可疑頻度","createTime":"2019-08-16T07:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:17:58.000Z","uid":184212,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8940fd762216b9e2caa9561a2f33a543cb66c50d","tid":1477551,"uid":184212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:12:13.000Z","msg":"(唔知有冇po過）<br />\n<br />\n重點：香港收緊好多疑似大陸電台，唔受OFCA規管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地識裝app上網聽廣播，但家中老人家就多數用收音機追台，唔使錢老人家最buy!<br />\n<br />\n剛剛幫住大圍既老媽子set返個收音機，一自動追台就發覺不得了，老牌電台（商台，港台，et）freq中間夾左勁多大6台，講咩祖國情懷，衰過睇cctvb，連我淺藍老媽子都頂唔順，所以先要驚動不俏子攪攪佢。<br />\n<br />\n請關心家中長者心靈健康！拒絕可疑頻度！<br />\n<br />\n請住九龍港島爸絲提供接收情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n1. 冇得set台既收音機，幫佢撥去港台/ 881/ 新城呢啲岩佢地聽既台<br />\n<br />\n2. 正確指導長者，頻度內容未受政府規管，可散佈假資訊<br />\n<br />\n3. 有得set台既，唔使講啦，自己睇OFCA個頻度表，做個孝順仔女<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ofca.gov.hk/filemanager/ofca/common//broadcasting/freq_table_sound_en.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ofca.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fofca%2Fcommon%2F%2Fbroadcasting%2Ffreq_table_sound_en.pdf&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=70843473\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ofca.gov.hk/filemanager/ofca/common//broadcasting/freq_table_sound_en.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"d3335a7270deee400cf94fee61794607a865c280","tid":1477551,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"你個人住得近大陸收到大陸台咋傻西<br />\n<br />\n縮返入庇護工場啦"},{"pid":"1ed1710287dc13db21aefe43b2a591651a783737","tid":1477551,"uid":279510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:2